about.summary: Utility function to fetch docker secrets/envvars.

name: get-docker-secret
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "get-docker-secret" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5f86039da59e9124ba4f9cb295851f91b136e6d044ae468d324aab689137f69c

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - get_docker_secret

about:
  home: https://github.com/fischerfredl/get-docker-secret
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Utility function to fetch docker secrets/envvars.
  dev_url: https://github.com/fischerfredl/get-docker-secret

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lincrosenbach
    - nicoddemus
    - nobreconfrade
